{"tid":679231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老鼠藥混湯畀60歲母親飲　天水圍30歲仔涉企圖謀殺被捕","createTime":"2018-05-26T16:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T05:15:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"937db0a2a4ea77c8bd808bfb55c42f844412fb29","tid":679231,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"天水圍發生企圖謀殺母親案！警方昨日接獲報案，指一名30歲姓吳男子懷疑於本月16日在天逸邨一單位，在湯內放入懷疑毒藥給其60歲姓周母親飲用。元朗警區重案組接手跟進，經初步調查，今日拘捕吳男，涉嫌企圖謀殺，他現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，吳男於案發當日替母親翻熱一碗湯，母親飲用後覺得有怪味，發現湯渣中有紅色粒狀物體，有人直認在街執了老鼠藥然後放入湯內，惟母親聞言後未有即時報案及求醫。至兩日後，母親帶兒子返回青山醫院覆診，並將事件告知醫生，直至昨日有人向警方報案揭發事件。"},{"pid":"6e5b5cafc67e014697afda10b3788499ddf06f34","tid":679231,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:36:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180526/58242034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F58242034&d=VFpzqY4A9DVe6GrG6Xv%2BaC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b4f56277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F58242034&h=6a8bd371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180526/58242034</a>"},{"pid":"82f35b1e82d0c8edf903f21a6dbb5d5ca6383307","tid":679231,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"連登孝子上新聞"},{"pid":"f3c7d8d77297a4098d0482ca5d583f7768e8b514","tid":679231,"uid":118120,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天水圍發生企圖謀殺母親案！警方昨日接獲報案，指一名30歲姓吳男子懷疑於本月16日在天逸邨一單位，在湯內放入懷疑毒藥給其60歲姓周母親飲用。元朗警區重案組接手跟進，經初步調查，今日拘捕吳男，涉嫌企圖謀殺，他現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，吳男於案發當日替母親翻熱一碗湯，母親飲用後覺得有怪味，發現湯渣中有紅色粒狀物體，有人直認在街執了老鼠藥然後放入湯內，惟母親聞言後未有即時報案及求醫。<span style=\"color: red;\">至兩日後，母親帶兒子返回青山醫院覆診</span>，並將事件告知醫生，直至昨日有人向警方報案揭發事件。</blockquote><br />\n痴線佬想謀老母身家"},{"pid":"b7b356d28059c52764c1a2f4f8fd4a95e4d986a3","tid":679231,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"精神病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347427242e2e85e5a59f6797469a4837a36f4fa1","tid":679231,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"啲咸豐年用嘅屎橋重拎出嚟用<br />\n笑都笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ee589eecfd79076ccc51590cf34912b91bcdb8","tid":679231,"uid":110745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"做左好多連登仔想做唔敢做既野"},{"pid":"549a99fea583d0f51f4a7951e8f86fa4d946725d","tid":679231,"uid":49853,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"食左老鼠藥都唔洗求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9874edad6b34ef83698c9dffffaf5c863cc8792","tid":679231,"uid":26084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:15:42.000Z","msg":"老母冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff8a0cbdea6f82e3285f69eab699818f8d09ef0","tid":679231,"uid":27247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"549a99fea583d0f51f4a7951e8f86fa4d946725d","tid":679231,"uid":49853,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"食左老鼠藥都唔洗求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:20:41.000Z","msg":"made in _"},{"pid":"810eb4a9af02de028e94f018a2c3a055d7530bb9